<title type="html"><![CDATA[Vertical scrolling offset &gt;255]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6305&amp;p=60197#p60197"><![CDATA[
Normally:  You go from scroll 239 on NT $2000 to scroll 0 on NT $2800<br /><br />But if you have a scroll over 239, then you go from 255 on NT $2000 to scroll 0 on NT $2000 (not $2800, which would be logical)<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=33">Disch</a> — Tue Apr 20, 2010 12:38 pm</p><hr />
